    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Si sacris et venerabilibus locis temporalia et transitoria
                        impendimus, eterna et sine fine mansura nos auxiliante Domino adipisci
                        nequaquam difidimus. Quapropter omnium [fidelium] sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet et futurorum noverit industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke"><name ref="Adalardus"
                            >Adelardum</name></persName> illustrem <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >marchionem</rs> dilectissimum <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem nostrum</rs>
                        nostram suppliciter exorasse <rs key="#Intercessory">clementiam</rs>,
                        quatenus <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Islands #Curtes #Fundi #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Mills #Churches #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/211">sancti Iohannis</orgName> intra hanc
                            <placeName ref="#places/65">Ticinensem civitatem</placeName> fundate
                        dignaremur concedere, confirmare et corroborare sub plenissima integritate
                        omnes res et possessiones quas ipsa ecclesia Sancti Iohannis tam per <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Inflow #Gift">donum</rs> sanctae memorie
                            <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/299">Gondiperge</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">reginae</rs>, que ipsam edificavit ecclesiam, quam per
                        precepta regum et imperatorum seu et firmitates aliorum religiosorum hominum
                        actenus habere et detinere dinoscitur. Cuius precibus aclinati, ita fieri
                        anuimus, huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis preceptum scribi
                        iubentes, [per quod] prenominate ecclesie Sancti Iohannis concedimus,
                        confirmamus et sub omni integritate coroboramus omnes res et possessiones
                        suas quas priscis temporibus tenuit et possedit, eo videlicet ordine, ut
                        ipsa ecclesia omnes res et possessiones suas, quas sibi per donum
                        prenominate regine et per precepta antecessorum nostrorum regum videlicet et
                        imperatorum et firmitates aliorum bonorum hominum possidere cernitur,
                        deinceps per hoc nostrum preceptum cum omni sua integritate teneat et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pleniter possideat</rs>, tam eas res et possessiones que ad partem
                        publicam regni nostri pertinuerunt quam et illas quas nostri antecessores,
                        reges videlicet et imperatores per sua precepta ob amorem Dei et sancti
                        Iohannis <rs key="#Canons">canonicis</rs> in ipsa ecclesia Deo militantibus
                        ad victum et vestimentum specialiter tribuerunt et denominative
                        concesserunt, videlicet infra menia huius Ticinensis [civitatis] <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >capellam</rs> unam <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Sancti Victoris</orgName> constructam cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >solario ante se et solariolum unum</rs> post tribunal prope <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes" ref="#estates/304">cortem Palatiolum</geogName>,
                            <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansiones duas</rs> penes <geogName key="#Houses #Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/305">cortem Genuensem</geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >salatiolum unum</rs> ante portam eiusdem ecclesie, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansiones duas</rs>, claustra in circuitu ecclesie cum viridatio extra
                        muros civitatis, <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >hortulos duos</rs> prope <orgName>basilicam Sancti Victoris</orgName>,
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >clausuram unam</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >campos tres</rs>, infra menia ipsius civitatis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >braidam unam</rs>, in <placeName key="#Hay/fodder" ref="#places/634"
                            >Nassaria</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pratellos quinque</rs>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Hay/fodder" ref="#places/635">Terra Arsa</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pratum unum</rs> simul cum <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >silvula</rs>, in <placeName>Monteferrato</placeName> in loco qui
                        dicitur <placeName key="#Islands #Mansi" ref="#places/636"
                            >Rivassi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos quinque</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Islands #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >insula infra Padum</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/637">in
                            Altruelini</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/638">in
                            Bertesassi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/639">in
                            Pulveria</placeName><rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            > mansum unum</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/640">in
                            Bucellade</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansum unum</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/641">in
                            Gebedi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansum unum</rs>, in loco qui nuncupatur <placeName key="#Mansi"
                            ref="#places/642">Archidiaconi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos septem</rs>, <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/643">in
                            Balbiano</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/43">civitate
                            Placentina</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >salatiolam unam</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >parvo horto</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >campo uno</rs>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName key="#Mansi #Churches"
                            ref="#places/644">Sancti Cipriani</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >capellam unam</rs> cum domo coltili et <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos quatuor</rs> et cum omni sua pertinentia, <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/645">in Segestri</placeName>
                        quandam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem terram</rs>, similiter <placeName ref="#places/646">in
                            Levarnia</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/647">in
                            Caurani</placeName> ac infra civitatem <placeName ref="#places/626"
                            >Genuesam</placeName> et in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/306">comitatu Terdonensi</geogName>, similiter in loco ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/648">Regiana</placeName>, <placeName
                            ref="#places/649">Mariana</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/650"
                            >Verlasca</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/651">Freneto</placeName>,
                            <placeName ref="#places/652">Cassiano</placeName>, nec non et <placeName
                            ref="#places/653">Topiole</placeName>, in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/307">comitatu Aquensi</geogName> in loco ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/654">Cuspiano</placeName> cum omni sua
                        integritate, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/655"
                            >Cavanasco</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos tres et absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi"
                            ref="#places/656">Frisosco</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/657"
                            >Bibiano</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/658"
                            >Miolaco</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi #Mills" ref="#places/659"
                            >Gambaro</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos duos</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >molendino</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/660"
                            >Moliana</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >manentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/661"
                            >Corliasco</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/662"
                            >Merlade</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/664"
                            >Visedano</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/663"
                            >Carponio</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/665"
                            >Frontinassi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/666"
                            >Grameneto</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/667"
                            >Turredano</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansum unum</rs>, in <placeName key="#Petiae #Wine" ref="#places/668"
                            >Aurello</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >petias de vitibus duas</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >campellum unum</rs>, <geogName key="#Curtes #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/311">cortem de Robationico</geogName> cum omnibus
                        pertinentiis suis et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Royal_slave"
                            >familiis utriusque sexus</rs> et districtionibus, in <placeName
                            key="#Royal_aldius" ref="#places/669">Carvina</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Royal_aldius"
                            >aldiones</rs> reddentes ceram ad luminaria prefate ecclesie, similiter
                        in <placeName ref="#places/670">Pino</placeName> et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/671">Canobio</placeName>, hec solumodo usui et utilitati
                        canonicorum pretaxate ecclesie que nuncupatur Domnarum, sicut alii nostri
                        antecessores reges et imperatores per sua precepta et alii religiosi et
                        sancti viri per suas firmitates concesserunt, in et nos per hoc nostrum
                        preceptum concedimus, confirmamus et pleniter coroboramus et perdonamus, ea
                        videlicet ratione, ut tam <persName key="#Archpriests"><name ref="Agibertus"
                                >Agevertus</name></persName> ipsius ecclesie <rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >archipresbiter</rs> et prepositus sibique subditi canonici quam et
                        eorum successores qui ibi pro tempore fuerint hec per huius nostre
                        auctoritatis donativum teneant ac possideant et exinde integram potestatem
                        habeant faciendi quicquid voluerint more ceterorum canonicorum, quatenus in
                        nostra mercede Deo et sancto Iohanni securi valeant deservire. Et si ipse
                        archipresbiter et prepositus vel successores eiusdem ecclesie ab hac luce
                        migraverit, non aliunde sed ex sinu ispius ecclesie sibi archipresbiterum et
                        prepositum eligant. Reliqua omnia ad eandem ecclesiam pertinentia pars
                        publica regni nostri per hoc nostrum pracmaticum pleniter teneat et cum omni
                        integritate possideat, sua omnium hominum inquietudine et contradictione
                        remota. Si quis igitur huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis preceptum
                        infringere vel violare aliquando presumpserit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras ducentum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem camere palatii nostri</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem parti ipsius
                            ecclesie Sancti Iohannis</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab
                        omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter iussimus
                        insigniri. Signum (M) domni Berengarii gloriosissimi regis. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data non. Kal. Iul.,
                        anno dominice incarnationis DCCCCVIIII, anno vero domni Berengarii
                        gloriosissimi regis XXII, indictione duodecima, Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName> palatii. In Christi nomine feliciter,
                        amen.</ab>
                </div>
